    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation for model risk level 3. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is accepted on the basis of regulatory precedent for single-condition ASTM F1717 submissions and the conservative nature of the selected load magnitude. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the intended regulatory use of the FEA model.",
